    ShapeDTO
    ShapeDTO is the representation of a line of tikz code, eg : \draw[thick,rounded corners=8pt] (0,0) -- (0,2) -- (1,3.25) -- (2,2) -- (2,0) -- (0,2) -- (2,2) -- (0,0) -- (2,0); In order to avoid confusion with an actual line (the shape line, who is called a path in tikz, still following ?) , it's called a shape here.
